invokeExportFilterMethod

public java.lang.Boolean invokeExportFilterMethod(javax.faces.component.UIComponent uiComponent,
                                                  oracle.adf.view.rich.export.ExportContext eContext,
                                                  oracle.adf.view.rich.export.FormatHandler fHandler)
exportCollectionActionListener invokes the default exportFilterMethod to convert NBSP(Â ) to SPACE( ) if grouping separator of session is NBSP and FND_CUSTOM_EXCEL_EXPORT is set to Y. Also calls the custom exportFilterMethod if provided and default exportFilterMethod hasn't already written the value to excel.

Parameters:
uiComponent - - component to be processed
eContext - - export context
fHandler - - format handler
Returns:
whether component needs to be handled by exportActionListener true if yes and false if already handled by exportFilter method.

getExportRowLimitOfTable

public java.lang.String getExportRowLimitOfTable()
Method to set rowLimit property for Export listener. If exportRowLimit property was not set at Table level, then it should be picked from Profile Option "FND_EXPORT_ROWLIMIT".

Returns:
export row count value
